---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Valgfag">

  <section class="bg-brand-50 py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-800 mb-4">Valgfag</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Vaelg det du brander for. Vores valgfag er skabt for at give dig mulighed for at dyrke dine interesser og opdage nye.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-brand-100 overflow-hidden hover:border-brand-400 transition-colors">
          <div class="h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-300 to-green-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <div class="text-center"><div class="text-6xl mb-2">&#x1F333;</div><p class="text-xl font-bold">Outdoor</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Vandreture, klatring, kajak og survival. Naturen er vores klassevaerrelse, og du laerer at mestre den med tryghed og begejstring.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Natur</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Teamwork</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Udfordring</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-brand-100 overflow-hidden hover:border-brand-400 transition-colors">
          <div class="h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-300 to-amber-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <div class="text-center"><div class="text-6xl mb-2">&#x1F528;</div><p class="text-xl font-bold">Metal og Trae</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Skab noget med dine haender. Savsmaeld, svejsning, traedrejning og konstruktion. Her goer du ideer til virkelighed.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Skabende</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Haandvaerk</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Design</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-brand-100 overflow-hidden hover:border-brand-400 transition-colors">
          <div class="h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-300 to-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <div class="text-center"><div class="text-6xl mb-2">&#x1F3AE;</div><p class="text-xl font-bold">E-sport</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Vaelg vores e-sport-linje og laer om strategi, teamwork og konkurrence. Vi spiller seriost men i godt selskab.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Gaming</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Strategi</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Teamwork</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-brand-100 overflow-hidden hover:border-brand-400 transition-colors">
          <div class="h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-300 to-pink-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <div class="text-center"><div class="text-6xl mb-2">&#x1F58C;&#xFE0F;</div><p class="text-xl font-bold">Kreativt</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Tegning, maleri, foto, grafisk design og teater. Udtryk dig selv paa maader der passer til dig.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Kunst</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Udtryk</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Design</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-brand-100 overflow-hidden hover:border-brand-400 transition-colors">
          <div class="h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-300 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <div class="text-center"><div class="text-6xl mb-2">&#x1F3B5;</div><p class="text-xl font-bold">Musik</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Spil et instrument, synge i kor, producere beats eller laer om lydteknik. Musik handler om at have det sjovt og udtrykke sig.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Sang</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Instrument</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Produktion</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-brand-100 overflow-hidden hover:border-brand-400 transition-colors">
          <div class="h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-300 to-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <div class="text-center"><div class="text-6xl mb-2">&#x26BD;</div><p class="text-xl font-bold">Sport</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Fodbold, haandbold, volleyball, styrketraening og meget mere. Sport handler ikke kun om at vinde, men om at have det godt i kroppen.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Hold</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Fitness</span>
              <span class="bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Sundhed</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-brand-50 py-16 px-4"><div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-800 mb-4">Vil du hoere mere om vores valgfag?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">Kontakt os og faa en snak om, hvad der passer bedst til dig.</p>
    <a href="/emmerske_clipcore/kontakt" class="inline-block px-10 py-4 bg-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-700 text-white text-xl font-semibold rounded-xl transition-colors shadow-md">Kontakt os</a>
  </div></section>

</Layout>